	abstract = {Registration is an important step when processing three-dimensional (3-D) point clouds. Applications for registration range from object modeling and tracking, to simultaneous localization and mapping (SLAM). This article presents the open-source point cloud library (PCL) and the tools available for point cloud registration.},
